<?xml version="1.0"?>
<package>
  <metadata>
    <id>Hangfire.SqlServer</id>
    <version>%version%</version>
    <title>Hangfire SQL Server Storage</title>
    <authors>Sergey Odinokov</authors>
    <owners>HangfireIO, odinserj</owners>
    <projectUrl>https://www.hangfire.io/</projectUrl>
    <repository type="git" url="https://github.com/HangfireIO/Hangfire.git" commit="%commit%" />
    <license type="file">LICENSE.md</license>
    <icon>icon.png</icon>
    <description>SQL Server 2008+ (including Express), SQL Server LocalDB and SQL Azure storage support for Hangfire, a background job framework for .NET applications.</description>
    <copyright>Copyright ¬© 2013-2026 Hangfire O√ú</copyright>
    <tags>Hangfire SqlServer SqlAzure LocalDB</tags>
    <releaseNotes><![CDATA[
Release notes are available in our blog https://www.hangfire.io/blog/
Please see https://docs.hangfire.io/en/latest/upgrade-guides/upgrading-to-hangfire-1.8.html to learn how to upgrade.

1.8.22
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď `InvalidCastException` when creating a background job with Schema 5 (regression from 1.8.15).
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Replace the `netcoreapp3.1` target with the `net8.0` one in tests.

1.8.21
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `SqlServerStorageOptions.DisableTransactionScope` option for .NET Framework targets.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Port Monitoring API tests from the Hangfire.InMemory storage for better coverage.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Run tests for different targets in parallel with different databases.

1.8.19
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Sliding invisibility timeout isn't prolonged in lightweight servers, causing jobs to be restarted.

1.8.17
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď `InvalidCastException` while fetching a job with older schemas regression from 1.8.16.

1.8.16
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use vanilla ADO.NET when fetching a job in the `SqlServerJobQueue` implementation.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď SqlException: Must declare the scalar variable "@key" in delayed and recurring job schedulers.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Decrease the `LockTimeout` time when calling the `sp_getapplock` procedure to 1 second for less blocking.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Disable parallel tests execution when building under .NET 9.0.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Run tests over the latest Microsoft.Data.SqlClient package and the `net6.0` platform.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Reduce execution time of integration tests.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Disable `PoolBlockingPeriod` setting on AppVeyor to handle transient test failures.

1.8.15
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use query template caching based on schema name to avoid excessive `string` allocations.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use static callbacks almost anywhere to avoid unnecessary delegate allocations.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use `QuerySingle`* or `ReadSingle`* where possible to avoid allocating lists.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Unify `DbCommand` and `DbParameter` creation logic to improve code consistency.

1.8.13 and 1.8.14
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Limit polling queries when queues are empty with a semaphore for all configurations.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use per-queue signaling for same-process workers, instead of having a global signal.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't silently truncate queue names, throw an exception instead.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Decrease delays in SQL Server-related tests to complete them faster.

1.8.12
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Populate `InvocationData` and `LoadException` properties in `JobDetails` method results.

1.8.10
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Bump Dapper for the `netstandard2.0` platform to version 2.1.28.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Bump Dapper for `net451` and `netstandard1.3` platforms to version 1.60.6.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Enable NuGet package and DLL signing with a company certificate.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Require NuGet package signature validation on restore for dependencies.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Add `HangfireIO` as a package owner.
      
1.8.9
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Enable full source link support with embedded symbols and repository-based sources.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Enable repeatable package restore using a lock file.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Run unit tests against the `net6.0` platform.

1.8.7
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Avoid throwing an exception when a connection string has duplicate property names.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Disable tests for `netcoreapp1.0` and `netcoreapp2.1` targets since they aren't supported in AppVeyor.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Add a `net6.0` target for unit tests instead of the removed ones.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Modernise projects and build environments to use the newest features.

1.8.6
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Exception in Dashboard UI when schema version is not present in a database.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď `DbCommand` resource leak when releasing a lock detected by static analysis.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't add SQL Server-related metrics multiple times in Dashboard UI.

1.8.5
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď "Query processor could not produce a query plan" when removing expired counters in `Schema 5`.

1.8.2
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď `InvalidOperationException` with new dashboard metrics when a database has multiple data/log files.

1.8.1
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Blocked workers regression since 1.7.33 when using multiple servers inside a process.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Target schema version is less than the current schema version error.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Implement database metrics without the need for additional permissions.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Use the `forceseek` table hint whenever possible to avoid performance drops.

1.8.0
‚ÄĘ Breaking ‚Äď Prioritise Microsoft.Data.SqlClient package over System.Data.SqlClient one.
‚ÄĘ Breaking ‚Äď Dropped the `NET45` platform target in favor of the `NET451` target to support Visual Studio 2022.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `Schema 8` migration with fixed `JobQueue.Id` column to use the `bigint` type.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `Schema 9` migration that creates an index for the `State.CreatedAt` column.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Automatic client package detection based on available types, preferring `System.Data.SqlClient` (by @0xced).
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `SqlServerStorageOptions.DbProviderFactory` option to use a custom provider factory.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Clean up of old state entries of a non-finished job when `InactiveStateExpirationTimeout` is set.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `TryAutoDetectSchemaDependentOptions` option to automatically enable options based on the schema.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Optional experimental transactional acknowledge for SQL Server (`UseTransactionalAcknowledge` option).
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Implement the `Connection.GetUtcDateTime` feature to make work the new changes in schedulers.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `SqlServerStorage.SchemaVersion` metric for Dashboard UI.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `DefaultQueueProvider` option to specify a custom default queue provider.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Remove dependency on System.Data.SqlClient for Hangfire.SqlServer (by @0xced).
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Set default value for the `QueuePollInterval` option to `TimeSpan.Zero`.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Polling delay when `QueuePollInterval` is set to zero now defaults to 200 ms.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Sliding invisibility timeout-based fetching method is now used by default with a 5-minute timeout.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use command batching by default with a 5-minute maximum timeout.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Enable the `UseRecommendedIsolationLevel` option by default.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď `GetJobData` now populates the `JobData.ParametersSnapshot` property to avoid additional roundtrips.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Display scheduled and processing jobs in ascending order in Dashboard UI.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Implement the `Transaction.AcquireDistributedLock` feature.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Implement the `GetSetCount.Limited feature`.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Implement the `GetSetContains feature`.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Bump the internal version of Dapper to 2.0.123.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Enable common metrics for SQL Server storage to be shown by default.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Enable the `Monitoring.AwaitingJobs` feature for SQL storage.
‚ÄĘ Deprecated ‚Äď `UsePageLocksOnDequeue` option is now obsolete and doesn't affect anything.
]]>
    </releaseNotes>
    <dependencies>
      <group targetFramework="net10.0">
        <dependency id="Hangfire.Core" version="[%version%]" />
      </group>
    </dependencies>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="net10.0\Hangfire.SqlServer.dll" target="lib\net10.0" />
